1
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,200
Ms. Xu, your outfit is so pretty.

2
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,200
Where did you buy it?

3
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,400
A friend gave it to me.

4
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,640
Don't tell me it's from your boyfriend.

5
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,560
No.

6
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,840
There's a movie coming out this Saturday

7
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,240
called 'Secret'.

8
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,000
I heard it's really good.

9
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,640
I don't have time to go.

10
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,050
I'm busy this Saturday.

11
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,320
I have time to watch it,

12
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,040
but

13
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,160
I need someone to go with.

14
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,260
Time for class.

15
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,480
I'm off.

16
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,740
Ms. Xu, I'm going to class.

17
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,520
Okay. I don't have a class this period.

18
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,680
I'll prepare my lessons here.

19
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,520
Okay.

20
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,120
Ms. Xu,

21
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,440
after preparing your lessons,

22
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,500
stretch your neck.

23
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,640
It's good for you.

24
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:41,800
Thanks.

25
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,640
I'm going to class.

26
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,200
Okay.

27
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,120
There's a movie coming out this Saturday

28
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,520
called "Secret".

29
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,400
Please welcome

30
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:32,410
the popular actress Xiong Yuanbao

31
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,640
to the stage.

32
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,640
Thank you, everyone. Thank you.

33
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,680
Thank you all.

34
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,890
No need for flowers.

35
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,690
Thank you for the applause.

36
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,480
First of all,

37
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,200
I want to thank my parents

38
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,400
for giving me such an artistic talent.

39
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,600
Then I also want to thank

40
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,400
my fans

41
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,680
for their enthusiastic support.

42
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,210
Thank you, my dear friends.

43
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,360
Thank you, everyone.

44
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,290
You are too kind.

45
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,000
Have a seat. Have a seat.

46
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,000
You are too kind.

47
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,320
Too kind. Too kind.

48
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,800
When did you get here?

49
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,970
No, how long have you been here?

50
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:15,770
Since your grand entrance.

51
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,420
Your acceptance speech was pretty good.

52
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,200
You're too kind.

53
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,480
This is pretty awkward.

54
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:34,920
Back at Peiying,

55
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,840
whenever we had PE class,

56
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:39,420
I'd come to the rooftop to enjoy the view.

57
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,840
Now at Zhicheng,

58
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:45,080
I didn't expect to meet a kindred spirit.

59
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,480
When Mutou and I were little,

60
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,320
we loved playing on the rooftop.

61
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,000
But he is afraid of heights,

62
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,360
so I always liked to scare him.

63
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,800
If he didn't listen to me,

64
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:58,020
I'd lock him on the roof and wouldn't let him go home.

65
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,540
Seems like you two are very close.

66
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,920
We grew up together.

67
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,160
What are you laughing at?

68
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,600
Don't move.

69
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:42,800
There is a leaf.

70
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:48,380
There's a leaf.

71
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,080
Damn.

72
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,180
Going to study.

73
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:07,800
Ms. Xu,

74
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,400
getting off work?

75
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,640
Yes.

76
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,140
Why is your face so red?

77
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,480
Are you sick?

78
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,480
See you at the cinema this weekend.

79
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:40,500
From someone who has admired you for a long time.

80
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,560
I...

81
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,570
Why is my heart beating so fast?

82
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,760
You don't understand.

83
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,220
I am no longer an immortal.

84
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,280
I...

85
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:02,780
You don't understand.

86
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,240
I am no longer...

87
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,000
You don't understand.

88
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,240
You...

89
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,280
Have some fruit and take a break.

90
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,210
I don't want any.

91
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,600
I mean,

92
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,360
just let it go.

93
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,760
You can't win anyway.

94
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,040
Just act casually.

95
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,680
Why are you so depressed?

96
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,560
You really are a jinx.

97
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:37,440
I knew it.

98
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,440
You never have anything nice to say.

99
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,360
Look at you.

100
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,720
You've been doing nothing but studying and practicing lines,

101
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,380
but why are you getting worse?

102
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:48,000
Are you too tired?

103
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,600
I don't know either.

104
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:53,000
The more anxious I get, the worse I memorize.

105
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,520
Alright.

106
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:59,050
Why don't you take a break today

107
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,200
and clear your mind?

108
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,760
I'll take you to a movie.

109
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:03,560
You need to balance work and rest.

110
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,420
I'm not going. I'm not in the mood.

111
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,440
Don't you want to go to the cinema

112
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,840
to observe how others act?

113
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,920
Besides,

114
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,720
it stars Jay Chou.

115
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,360
Jay Chou?

116
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,520
Not bad.

117
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,360
Hello, I'm Jay Chou.

118
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,130
Do you want to go?

119
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,370
You should've told me earlier.

120
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,720
When?

121
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,880
You go out first. I need to change.

122
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:30,640
Hurry!

123
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,720
Hello, Mr. Xu.

124
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,920
Mr. Xu is here.

125
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,720
It's all your fault.

126
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,000
Why did we have to wait for the 315?

127
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,060
If we took the 414, we'd be here by now.

128
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:09,920
What's the rush?

129
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,720
There's still a line over there.

130
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,400
Hurry up.

131
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,440
Two buckets of popcorn.

132
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,040
Wait a minute.

133
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,840
Hurry and pay.

134
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,080
Don't rush.

135
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,410
What's the rush?

136
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,680
Mr. Xu.

137
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:40,520
Hello.

138
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:04,600
Why are these two kids here?

139
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,720
If they find out I'm watching a movie with Mr. Xu,

140
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,980
it would be so awkward.

141
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,940
Excuse me, sir.

142
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,600
Are you in the wrong seat?

143
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,320
Mr. Tian.

144
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,680
Tian Yong.

145
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,160
Mr. Liu Li.

146
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,160
Well,

147
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,160
Mr. Liu and I are just

148
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,720
doing a surprise inspection at the movie theater today,

149
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,400
to see if there are any

150
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,730
boys and girls watching movies together.

151
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:12,400
And I actually caught a pair.

152
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,280
Yes, exactly.

153
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,640
Well, Mr. Tian, Mr. Liu.

154
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,840
We've been studying all morning.

155
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,600
Really.

156
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,720
Isn't the drama festival coming up soon?

157
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:25,200
We just wanted to strike a balance between work and rest,

158
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,040
so we came out to watch a movie.

159
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:27,920
To learn.

160
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:28,920
To learn.

161
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:29,960
Right.

162
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:31,360
Well,

163
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,680
since that's the case, it's excusable.

164
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,530
They are still kids.

165
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,320
They're childhood sweethearts,

166
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,520
so it's normal for them to be playful.

167
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,120
Right?

168
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,560
Mr. Tian, I think we should just drop this.

169
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:43,360
Let's all go our separate ways.

170
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,560
Hurry up and leave.

171
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,600
Are you waiting for me to scold you?

172
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:47,720
Okay, goodbye, sir.

173
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,440
Thank you.

174
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:49,920
Let's go.

175
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:03,000
You're right.

176
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,280
Go that way.

177
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,040
That way.

178
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,760
I'm so lucky to see such a scene in my life.

179
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:13,520
The movie doesn't even matter anymore.

180
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:18,060
What are you thinking about every day in that little head of yours?

181
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,320
Say,

182
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,640
if one day in the future,

183
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,960
we could also make movies...

184
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,160
If the movies we made

185
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:30,050
could be shown in theaters,

186
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,920
how would that feel?

187
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,720
What?

188
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,840
Do you want to be an actor

189
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,900
or a screenwriter?

190
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:40,050
A screenwriter, of course.

191
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:42,520
But I need to understand actors too.

192
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,400
If one day,

193
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,240
a movie I wrote

194
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,760
could be shown on the big screen,

195
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,360
I would wake up laughing from my dreams.

196
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:59,920
So do you really like 'A Chinese Odyssey' this time,

197
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:03,320
or is it because of that Meng Jingu?

198
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:07,730
First of all, of course it's because I like 'A Chinese Odyssey'.

199
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,120
But secondly,

200
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,800
if I could act with someone

201
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:13,680
as excellent as Meng Jingu,

202
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,920
that would be great too.

203
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,360
However...

204
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,320
Mutou,

205
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,720
tell me,

206
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,480
am I really useless?

207
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:39,380
Why would you suddenly say that about yourself?

208
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:48,560
Look, I've been memorizing for so many days,

209
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:51,120
yet I can't even remember a few lines,

210
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,840
let alone perform on stage.

211
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,560
I suddenly feel

212
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,130
like I can't do anything right.

213
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:01,160
All I do is daydream all day.

214
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:09,120
Yuanbao, don't cry.

215
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:11,490
You're not as bad as you say you are.

216
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:17,620
You said this morning that I would definitely lose.

217
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,440
Actually, I feel the same way.

218
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:23,600
Actually, I was just kidding, Yuanbao.

219
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,480
You are really great.

220
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:28,360
You have to believe in yourself.

221
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,680
Do you remember when we were in junior high

222
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,120
and performed a magic trick together?

223
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:34,880
I remember you were so nervous before going on stage,

224
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:37,600
but you performed really well once you were up there.

225
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:40,080
You've just been putting too much pressure on yourself lately.

226
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:42,480
You want to do too well in this performance.

227
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:44,720
Really?

228
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,160
Of course.

229
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:47,560
Listen to me.

230
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,200
I'll teach you how to relax your face.

231
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,920
I see actors before going on stage

232
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,760
doing these facial relaxation

233
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:03,440
and

234
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,840
warm-up exercises.

235
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,040
Come on, do it with me.

236
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:17,100
Do you feel better?

237
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:20,480
How about this, I'll practice with you.

238
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:23,080
Even if it's last-minute, it might still help.

239
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:26,040
Aren't you acting with Xing Yaqi?

240
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:28,640
Why are you willing to practice with me now?

241
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:31,000
I'm trying to help you, aren't I?

242
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,440
Are you going to practice or not?

243
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,240
I will.

244
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:34,760
But...

245
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:37,080
there are so many people here.

246
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,960
Isn't a performance meant to be seen by everyone?

247
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,320
It's also a good way to build your courage.

248
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,680
Come on, I'll start.

249
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:46,480
Once there was a sincere love

250
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,480
placed before me,

251
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:49,410
but I didn't cherish it.

252
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,920
Zhi Zunbao, wait for me.

253
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:54,080
I only regretted it after losing it.

254
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,780
There is nothing more painful in this world.

255
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,720
Just cut my throat with your blade.

256
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,920
What?

257
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:01,720
What are your next lines?

258
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,930
I don't know either.

259
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,840
Grandma.

260
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:19,180
Why are there so many bottles?

261
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,920
The price of plastic has gone up recently.

262
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,200
I need to collect more.

263
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,170
I can sell them for a lot more money.

264
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,640
I'll help you.

265
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,020
I'll help Grandma.

266
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:29,290
You help carry this.

267
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,960
Grandma, just give it to me.

268
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:16,720
Come on.

269
00:17:17,040 --> 00:17:18,599
Young people nowadays

270
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,210
don't know how to do chores.

271
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:21,560
Trust me, Grandma.

272
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:22,640
I can do it.

273
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,280
Go.

274
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:26,560
Go study.

275
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:29,280
Grandma, I'm done with my homework.

276
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:30,480
You've been busy all day.

277
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,000
Leave it to me.

278
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,480
Take a good rest, okay?

279
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:33,880
Oh, you child.

280
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:36,320
Your focus right now should be on studying.

281
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:38,520
Grandma.

282
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,660
Grandma, look.

283
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:40,720
Your precious granddaughter

284
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,650
has prepared the footbath for you.

285
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,800
Go ahead.

286
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,800
How's the water temperature?

287
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:52,880
Just right.

288
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,320
My Yuanbao has grown up.

289
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:59,800
You know how to care for Grandma now.

290
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:00,880
Of course.

291
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,840
Grandma is my goddess.

292
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:07,040
Yes, we are all goddesses.

293
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:09,920
You are a little goddess.

294
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,560
And Grandma is an old goddess.

295
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:17,940
Do you remember

296
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:20,960
when you couldn't sleep as a child,

297
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,120
Grandma would sing to you?

298
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:30,080
The moon is bright, the wind is still.

299
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:35,560
Leaves cover the window lattice.

300
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:41,520
The little baby is called Zhengzheng.

301
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:47,000
Quickly close your eyes.

302
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:52,960
The wind is still, the moon is bright.

303
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:57,760
The cradle swings gently.

304
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:01,720
You've been

305
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:03,410
in a bad mood these days.

306
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,600
I failed my exam.

307
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:07,220
When my mom beat me that day, her wig fell off.

308
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:10,120
I just realized she's been wearing a wig for so long.

309
00:19:10,120 --> 00:19:11,850
Her hair loss is quite serious.

310
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:17,680
Then you should study hard from now on

311
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,720
and make your mom worry less.

312
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:22,930
I've made up my mind.

313
00:19:24,120 --> 00:19:26,160
I'll play fewer games from now on.

314
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:28,840
You sounded so determined,

315
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:31,440
I thought you were going to quit playing games.

316
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,920
That would be so boring.

317
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,660
Bro, let's talk about you.

318
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:38,960
The roles are about to be cast.

319
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,160
Are you sure?

320
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,960
To prevent Yuanbao from acting with Meng Jingu,

321
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,440
you've taken a lot of trouble.

322
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,440
What if

323
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:50,040
Yuanbao really can't play Fairy Zixia?

324
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:51,760
Will she be sad?

325
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,600
I'm also worried about this.

326
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:57,080
Let me say something unpleasant.

327
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,120
Go ahead.

328
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:00,840
You are just jealous.

329
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,280
That's really unpleasant.

330
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,520
Envy?

331
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:05,800
Jealousy?

332
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:07,320
Of Meng Jingu?

333
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:10,120
Are you out of your mind?

334
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,920
He's just taller and more handsome,

335
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,980
has better grades,

336
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:16,040
and comes from a better family.

337
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,280
I used to go to the same school as him.

338
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:18,680
He is quite a good person.

339
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:20,520
Last time, it was close to the monthly exam

340
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:22,000
when you gave Yuanbao the review materials.

341
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,200
What about this time?

342
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:24,120
Go quickly.

343
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:25,280
If it doesn't work,

344
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:27,610
just send it to her anonymously via email.

345
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:31,280
Didn't you ask me to come over to discuss countermeasures?

346
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,410
Then... I'll leave.

347
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:39,400
Hello.

348
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,060
Is this Cool Bear's house?

349
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,600
Yes, I'm Cool Bear's grandmother.

350
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,640
Here is your package.

351
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,480
Thank you.

352
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:52,240
Cool Bear, your package.

353
00:20:52,280 --> 00:20:53,480
What is it, Grandma?

354
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:55,500
It's yours. Why are you asking me?

355
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,240
Put this on,

356
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:08,290
and you'll be the most beautiful Fairy Zixia.

357
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:09,960
I look forward to

358
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:13,580
Yuanbao's version of Fairy Zixia even more.

359
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,160
Come on, Yuanbao.

360
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:32,120
Looking forward to your performance tomorrow.

361
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:34,120
I chose a few good clips

362
00:21:34,520 --> 00:21:35,960
and printed out the corresponding lines.

363
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:36,840
Take a look.

364
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:38,920
I know an acting coach.

365
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:40,540
Are you free after school?

366
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:42,240
I can ask her to give you some guidance.

367
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:43,300
Let's go together.

368
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,640
Meng Jingu is so thoughtful.

369
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,440
Thank you, desk mate.

370
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:51,240
You are awesome.

371
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,170
I will do my best.

372
00:21:58,840 --> 00:22:00,680
Okay, I will let you go.

373
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,400
But you must kiss me.

374
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:10,480
Jingu, stop playing with your phone.

375
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,140
I have something to say to you.

376
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:14,520
Your freshman year is coming to an end soon.

377
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:17,200
You'll also be divided into arts and science classes soon.

378
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:19,280
I communicated with your homeroom teacher.

379
00:22:19,280 --> 00:22:20,720
With your current grades,

380
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,840
getting into the top science class won't be a problem.

381
00:22:22,840 --> 00:22:25,120
Since you dislike finance so much,

382
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:27,120
I won't force you.

383
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:29,720
I am an open-minded father.

384
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,960
Since you want to study physics,

385
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,760
I will respect your wishes.

386
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,560
Really?

387
00:22:36,360 --> 00:22:37,160
However,

388
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,920
I have a condition.

389
00:22:39,560 --> 00:22:40,680
My requirement is

390
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,770
that you must become the top science student.

391
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:46,080
My son can only be first,

392
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,160
never second.

393
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:48,760
Got it?

394
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:55,120
Quiet down, class.

395
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:57,480
We'll use this study hall

396
00:22:58,080 --> 00:23:00,280
to vote and decide

397
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:02,360
on the roles for the drama competition.

398
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,620
I'll give you 5 minutes

399
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,520
to prepare,

400
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,640
then we'll start.

401
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:06,840
Okay.

402
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:10,040
Don't be nervous. Relax.

403
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,660
Mu Qingjun isn't here yet.

404
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,200
All right, class.

405
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:26,100
Our first group is going on stage.

406
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:29,800
You insolent monkey.

407
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:33,640
To marry the Bull Demon King's sister.

408
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:41,600
Why are you here?

409
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,720
You're talking nonsense again.

410
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,160
You're talking nonsense again.

411
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:49,280
Next, please welcome Xiong Yuanbao and Meng Jingu to the stage.

412
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:50,960
Don't be nervous.

413
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,400
Not bad.

414
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,410
Yuanbao, this is so beautiful.

415
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:14,960
Zhi Zunbao, you bastard.

416
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,760
Come out here!

417
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,080
Zhi Zunbao!

418
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,720
You bastard!

419
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,280
Come out here!

420
00:24:29,320 --> 00:24:30,360
I'm right here.

421
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,170
It seems I shouldn't have come.

422
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:39,500
It's too late to realize that now.

423
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,480
Can't we leave some memories?

424
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:43,080
I don't want to leave memories.

425
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:46,010
If you want to leave something, leave yourself here.

426
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:48,840
Okay.

427
00:24:49,280 --> 00:24:50,480
Thank you, everyone.

428
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:55,020
Mu Qingyun isn't here yet.

429
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:57,000
What kind of person is he?

430
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:09,560
Next, please welcome the final group.

431
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:12,040
Mu Qingyun, Xing Yaqi.

432
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:19,240
Take another half step forward,

433
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,560
and I'll kill you.

434
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,240
You should do this.

435
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,800
And I deserve to die.

436
00:25:27,080 --> 00:25:28,640
There was once a sincere love

437
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,800
placed before me,

438
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:32,170
but I didn't cherish it.

439
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:36,600
Yuanbao really can't play Fairy Zixia anymore.

440
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:37,760
Will she be sad?

441
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,720
Yuanbao has been working so hard lately.

442
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,450
I've been memorizing for days,

443
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:44,720
but I can't even memorize a few lines,

444
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:46,250
let alone perform on stage.

445
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,120
I suddenly feel like

446
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,680
I can't do anything right.

447
00:25:52,600 --> 00:25:54,640
All I do is daydream all day.

448
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,200
Why isn't he saying anything?

449
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:09,480
Did he get too nervous and forget his lines?

450
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,000
No way.

451
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:12,600
I saw him running lines with the class monitor a couple of days ago,

452
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:13,840
and he was really fluent.

453
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,720
In that case,

454
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,240
then why did he...

455
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:20,800
I...

456
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,680
forgot my lines.

457
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:32,760
It's okay.

458
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,000
Take a moment to prepare,

459
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,130
and let's try again.

460
00:26:36,040 --> 00:26:37,240
Um, Mr. Tian,

461
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,010
no need to try again.

462
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,600
I don't think I'm capable

463
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:42,460
of playing the role of Zhi Zun Bao.

464
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,840
Yaqi.

465
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:51,400
I'm sorry

466
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,340
for dragging you down.

467
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:56,160
Qingyun, are you okay?

468
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:57,760
I'm fine.

469
00:27:16,520 --> 00:27:19,240
Mr. Tian, I just remembered

470
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:21,360
I have a vocal grading exam.

471
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:22,880
So,

472
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:24,700
I can't act either.

473
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,560
Okay.

474
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:27,440
Okay.

475
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:29,400
Jingu, congratulations.

476
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:06,280
Where did you go today?

477
00:28:06,520 --> 00:28:07,880
I sent you so many messages,

478
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,080
but you didn't reply.

479
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:12,720
I was playing games. I didn't see them.

480
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:16,240
Didn't you swear a few days ago

481
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:18,010
that you would beat Meng Jingu?

482
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:20,370
Why did you suddenly give up today?

483
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:23,380
What's wrong? Is something on your mind?

484
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:24,680
Nothing.

485
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:27,920
I just suddenly didn't want to act anymore.

486
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,400
Congratulations. You got what you wanted.

487
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:35,440
If you and Yaqi had participated,

488
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:39,500
I probably wouldn't have stood a chance.

489
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:42,960
Wait.

490
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:47,080
Did you withdraw just so

491
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,600
I could win?

492
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,560
You wish.

493
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,720
You know I've never liked

494
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,530
these kinds of activities.

495
00:28:59,280 --> 00:29:00,000
Besides,

496
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:02,120
I'm the top guy at Zhicheng.

497
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,800
Why would I act like an idiot

498
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:06,280
and play a monkey?

499
00:29:07,560 --> 00:29:08,160
See,

500
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:09,880
I knew it.

501
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,560
You've always been like this.

502
00:29:11,560 --> 00:29:13,760
When you suddenly said you were going to participate,

503
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:14,920
I was confused.

504
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:17,340
Now you're back to normal.

505
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:18,720
By the way,

506
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,600
I didn't tell Grandma

507
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:23,040
that I was staying at school to rehearse the play.

508
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:24,320
I just told her

509
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:26,740
Meng Jingu was tutoring me at school.

510
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:29,250
You have to keep this secret for me.

511
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:33,120
I got it.

512
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:37,240
Why are you agreeing so easily today?

513
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:41,280
Let's go home.

514
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,280
Grandma, I'm back.

515
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:50,800
Yuanbao is back.

516
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,880
Go wash your hands. We'll eat soon.

517
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:03,260
Thank you for the clothes.

518
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:07,560
These clothes really look good.

519
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:10,130
I didn't expect you to rent clothes yourself.

520
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:14,480
Yeah, yeah.

521
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:39,560
Grandma, I'm going out for a bit.

522
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:55,960
Eight thirty.

523
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:58,280
I'll wait for you at Jufeng Billiards Hall.

524
00:30:58,280 --> 00:30:59,240
See you there.

525
00:31:22,560 --> 00:31:23,320
Hello, boss.

526
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,320
I want to ask,

527
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:26,200
was this rented here?

528
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:27,520
It's ours.

529
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,800
Are you returning it?

530
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:31,760
I want to check the rental record

531
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:33,140
to see when it expires.

532
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,160
I want to rent more clothes.

533
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:36,800
Okay, wait a moment.

534
00:31:40,280 --> 00:31:42,010
There are still a few days left.

535
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:44,360
Here.
